                            Ranking

                Business query
Rank countries by: 
Risk (cases)
Prevention gap 

            Query
SELECT
	country_name,
	MAX(possible_cancer_cases)high_cases,
	RANK() OVER (ORDER BY MAX(possible_cancer_cases)DESC)ranked_cases
FROM cancer_data
GROUP BY country_name;

             QUERY
SELECT
	country_name,
	MAX(cancer_prevented) - MAX(deaths_prevented)gaps,
	RANK() OVER(ORDER BY MAX(cancer_prevented) - MAX(deaths_prevented)DESC)Prevented_gap
FROM cancer_data
GROUP BY country_name;


Insight
The prevention gap shows how many people are still dying when they could have been saved.

 Recommendation
Countries with the largest gap need urgent investment in healthcare systems.

